OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCool and
OL,6,Frather cloudy conditions persist into
OL,7,Fthe evening, with showers possible at
OL,8,Ftimes. Overnight these will ease,
OL,9,Fbecoming generally dry. Where cloud
OL,10,Fbreaks occur, there could be a rural
OL,11,Ffrost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FVariable cloud to start, but
OL,14,Fstaying mostly dry in the morning.
OL,15,FSunny spells and also a risk of
OL,16,Fshowers for the afternoon, but feeling
OL,17,Fgenerally warmer than Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
