OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday
OL,6,Fbrings sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers. Confidence lowers into the
OL,8,Fweekend, though rain or showers are
OL,9,Flikely on Saturday as well. Sunday
OL,10,Fappears drier, with occasional sunny
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
